Win with GLAMOUR and Sir Fruit Brewed Ice Tea|http://www.glamour.co.za|https://www.glamour.co.za/2018/10/win-with-glamour-and-sir-fruit-brewed-ice-tea/|Win|2018-10-04|October||In the mood to win a months worth of ice tea? Well, GLAMOUR and Sir Fruit Brewed Ice Tea have just the thing for you!

South Africa’s favourite premium fruit juice company is at it again with an all-new offering to tantalize the taste buds of ice tea lovers nationwide. Introducing Sir Fruit’s new real brewed, real bold, real low sugar Ice Tea!

Sir Fruit Brewed Ice Tea is brimming with taste and boasts one of the lowest sugar levels to be found in any similar beverage today. That’s because it’s traditionally brewed and uses only freshly sourced tea leaves and flavours.

So, settle in and sip on the natural goodness of locally gathered Rooibos, Honeybush, and Hibiscus – as well as imported Assam and Chinese Green Tea.

Want to be 1 of 9 winners to win a month’s supply of Sir Fruit Brewed Ice Tea to the value of R600? Simply fill in the form below to stand a chance:

